@host = http://localhost:8088
@endpoint = {{host}}/responses

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/readiness

### Simple string input
POST {{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "input": "Hi! I need help understanding the return policy."
}

### Explicit input
POST {{endpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
    "input": [
        {
            "type": "message",
            "role": "user",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "input_text",
                    "text": "How long does standard shipping usually take?"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
